    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《浣熊兰迪》可能不是画面最精致的游戏，但绝对充满个性。来看看是什么让它如此与众不同：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种疯狂武器任你使用，比如气球枪、臭味龙卷风，还有一台像灯光吸引蚊子一样吸引人类的收音机。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大量人类在街上走动，等你用武器测试，或者简单粗暴地撞一下就跑。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一群搞笑的动物等你聊天和接任务，比如疯鸡哥、修车员奇普、邪教领袖水豚君等等。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >互动地图，整个地图充满了可以互动的元素：例如只能承受一定重量的悬崖、巨型弹射器、可以越滚越大的雪球等等。结合你的武器，制造各种花样折磨 NPC！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有更多精彩内容等你探索！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦝 <strong>一只浣熊，有态度！</strong> <br>兰迪可不是普通的浣熊——他有自己的看法，而且一点也不怕表达出来！撞墙了？他会喊“哎哟！” 跳水了？他会怪你把他弄湿了。每一次碰撞、特技或搞笑时刻，兰迪都会配上标志性的吐槽和夸张反应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187000/extras/bd5a364d11e2200d29ccea020f105d2e.poster.avif?t=1768596123\" width=790 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187000/extras/bd5a364d11e2200d29ccea020f105d2e.webm?t=1768596123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187000/extras/bd5a364d11e2200d29ccea020f105d2e.mp4?t=1768596123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌎 <strong>一个充满活力的开放世界</strong> <br>探索一个广阔多彩的岛屿，认识性格各异的 NPC，完成各种任务。从毒舌动物到臭名昭著的鹅帮，每一个角落都藏着惊喜和乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187000/extras/ca3cae34477145891ac70826116bcc0f.poster.avif?t=1768596123\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187000/extras/ca3cae34477145891ac70826116bcc0f.webm?t=1768596123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187000/extras/ca3cae34477145891ac70826116bcc0f.mp4?t=1768596123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚗 <strong>你的车，你做主</strong> <br>改装你的座驾，打造属于你的混乱风格。加上跳跃装置、提升速度，或者喷个让兰迪满意的“独特”配色。这不只是代步工具，而是制造混乱的武器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187000/extras/5df3cc96b7ea0fa9e007f1891b630bf0.poster.avif?t=1768596123\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187000/extras/5df3cc96b7ea0fa9e007f1891b630bf0.webm?t=1768596123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187000/extras/5df3cc96b7ea0fa9e007f1891b630bf0.mp4?t=1768596123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
